				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The backpack you get is through the /claim function. It has only one upgrade....it goes from the 25% wt red to the 50% wt red...and atm thats it. 
<br />

<br />
It doesnt change stats...doesnt do anything else besides that. There is a rumor that it can someday be upgraded to 100% wt red...but no one has found the quest to do so.(atleast to my knowledge)
<br />

<br />
The adventures stone  is the only ldon item atm that changes stats as you go through the adventures.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps...<br />_________________<br />Lemba  Nameless
<br />

<br />
