<br />
Heh . .we were all new once ..
<br />

<br />
The upgraded sachel quest is: <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2642" target="_blank" class="postlink">Reinforced Satchel of Abu-Kar</a>
<br />

<br />
On the Adventure stones, you need to hail a particular NPC in each camp to get the increases to the adventure stone.  
<br />

<br />
For the first 10 wins you hail the following folks
<br />
BB - Vual Stoutest
<br />
South Ro - Selephra Giztral
<br />
Everfrost - Teria Grinntli
<br />
North Ro - Ruanya Windleaf
<br />
EC - Barstre Songweaver
<br />
At some point they will send you to talk to someone else to get the information.
<br />

<br />
For every 2 wins in a given camp, you'll receive a "valuable piece of information".  After 10 wins in a given camp you will gain a stat to your adventure stone.  The stone maxes out a a different number of wins per camp .. the information is in one of the posts on these boards I believe.
<br />

<br />
Maxed out stats are:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">AC: +10 Str: +10 Dex: +10 Sta: +10 Cha: +10 Wis: +10 Int: +10 Agi: +10 Fire Resist: +10 Disease Resist: +10 Cold Resist: +10 Magic Resist: +10 Poison Resist: +10 HP: +100 Mana: +100</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
I believe the recommended level is 65 so you'll see reduced stats if you're lower.  
<br />

<br />
Oh! And you have to put it on a charm to get the effects.  But if you delete that charm, just hail one of the guys above and you'll get your stone back.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps!<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=355393" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.catcreations.com/ariaya/images/AriayaSig.jpg" border="0" />
<br />
Magelo Profile</a></span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
